[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0100","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0100.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0039","title":"SGI IRIX webdist.cgi 命令执行漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.3 的 webdist.cgi 程序存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者通过在 distloc 参数中注入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符），即可绕过输入过滤执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.3 版本，攻击无需身份认证，仅需向目标 Web 服务发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发，可导致服务器被完全控制。CVSS 评分 7.3，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0039"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:25.717","remediation":"建议从 SGI 安全公告 19970501-02-PX 获取并安装对应 IRIX 版本的补丁。如无法立即打补丁，应删除或禁用 CGI 目录下的 webdist.cgi 程序，并确保 webdist 服务已停止。对于仍在使用 SGI IRIX 的系统，建议迁移至受支持的操作系统，因为 IRIX 已于 2006 年 12 月停止技术支持，不再提供安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1997-12.html","http://www.osvdb.org/235","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/374","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/333","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19299","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0039.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0039","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f47735aa52980ccd9473eed79b62a27c199a2cfa/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0039.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0039.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0039.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/webdist.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-j78w-x657-xvr7/GHSA-j78w-x657-xvr7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0039.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.1175"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0100.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0100.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0100.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0099","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0099.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0035","title":"多厂商 Unix ftpd 信号处理竞态条件漏洞","description":"ftpd 守护进程的信号处理例程中存在条件竞争漏洞（Race Condition），攻击者可利用信号处理时序差绕过文件访问控制，实现任意文件读取或写入。该漏洞影响多个 UNIX 系统中的 ftpd 实现，攻击者需与目标建立 FTP 连接并在特定操作窗口内触发竞态条件以完成利用，CVSS 评分 5.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0035"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-05-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:24.893","remediation":"升级 wu-ftpd 至 2.5.0 或更高版本，该版本修复了信号处理例程中的条件竞争问题。如无法升级，建议禁用 FTP 服务（systemctl disable vsftpd/wu-ftpd）或替换为 vsftpd/ProFTPD 等更安全的 FTP 守护进程。在不必要的情况下，可通过防火墙限制对 21 端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0035"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0099.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0098","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0098.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0433","title":"XFree86 startx 符号链接漏洞","description":"XFree86 中的 startx 命令存在符号链接（Symlink）漏洞，本地攻击者可通过在受限目录中创建恶意符号链接，利用该漏洞以提升的权限在目标目录中创建或覆盖任意文件，可能导致权限提升或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 X11R6 3.3.3 及之前版本，需攻击者具备本地系统访问权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0433"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.133","remediation":"升级到 XFree86 3.3.4 或更高版本，该版本修复了 startx 的符号链接处理问题。当前系统应使用 X.Org Server 替代已停止维护的 XFree86，并确保以非 root 权限运行 X 服务。对于老旧系统，可限制本地用户对 /tmp 共享目录的写入权限作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0433","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19257"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0098.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0098.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0097","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0097.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0432","title":"HP HP-UX FTP 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 11.00 操作系统的 FTP 服务存在权限提升漏洞，本地用户可利用该漏洞获取更高系统权限。由于 FTP 程序对用户权限校验不严格，已获得本地账户的攻击者登录系统后，可通过 FTP 工具的权限缺陷突破访问限制，获取非授权的文件读取或操作权限。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 11.00 版本，CVSS v2 评分 4.6，危害等级中等，攻击复杂度低。HP 已发布安全公告 HPSBUX9903-094 并提供修复方案。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0432"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:23.010","remediation":"立即安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9903-094 提供的对应补丁包（HP-UX 11.00 ftp 权限提升补丁）。如无法立即修补，可临时移除 /usr/bin/ftp 文件的 SUID 权限：执行 chmod 555 /usr/bin/ftp 阻止非授权用户以特权身份执行 ftp 命令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9903-094"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0097.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0096","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0096.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0036","title":"SGI IRIX login 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.4 及之前版本中的 /bin/login 程序存在本地权限提升漏洞。当 LOCKOUT 参数设置为非零值时，攻击者可通过精心构造的输入触发缓冲区溢出，以 root 权限创建或破坏系统文件，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞需要攻击者拥有本地 shell 访问权限，利用门槛较低，危害严重。SGI 已发布安全补丁修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0036"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:25.110","remediation":"立即安装 SGI 1997 年 5 月安全公告 19970508-02-PX 提供的修补补丁。临时缓解措施：在 /etc/default/login 配置文件中将 LOCKOUT 参数设为 0 并重启 login 服务。由于 SGI IRIX 已停止技术支持多年，建议尽快迁移至仍受支持的操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/h-106.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/990","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/557","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19310","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f47735aa52980ccd9473eed79b62a27c199a2cfa/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/SSVC/data/1999/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0036","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/dcc6735c9c3e50e93de820fa1ac9c54ecf6b2577/1999/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-00xx/CVE-1999-0036.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0096.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0095","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0095.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0033","title":"Sun Solaris at 程序缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun 系统的 at 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，由于对用户输入数据长度校验不严，本地攻击者可向 at 程序提交特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意命令，实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 SunOS、UnixWare、Open Desktop、OpenServer 等多个 Unix 操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。仅需本地账户即可利用，无需认证。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0033"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-06-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:24.453","remediation":"立即升级 Sun Solaris 至 2.5.1 及以上安全补丁版本，或安装 Sun 发布的对应安全补丁（如 105830-xx 系列）。对于 UnixWare/OpenServer 等受影响系统，升级至厂商修复版本。临时缓解措施：移除 at 程序的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/at），或通过编辑 cron.allow/at.allow 文件严格限制可执行 at 命令的用户白名单。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0033"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0095.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0094","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0094.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0032","title":"BSD系统 lpr 缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"BSD 系统的 lpr 打印服务存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向带 -C（分类）选项的 lpr 命令传入超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 BSD/OS 2.1、FreeBSD 2.1.5、NeXTstep 4.x、IRIX 6.4、SunOS 4.1.3/4.1.4 等基于 BSD 的系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0032"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-10-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:23.833","remediation":"建议将系统升级至已修复该漏洞的版本（FreeBSD 2.2 及以上、BSD/OS 3.0 及以上、IRIX 6.5 及以上），或应用厂商补丁替换存在缓冲区溢出的 lpr 二进制。如无法升级，可通过移除 lpr 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/lpr）限制本地普通用户提权，或改用 cups-lpr 等现代打印系统替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/i-042.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/707"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0094.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0093","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0093.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0031","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer JavaScript 信息泄露漏洞","description":"JavaScript 同源策略绕过漏洞存在于 Internet Explorer 3.x/4.x 及 Netscape 2.x/3.x/4.x 等早期浏览器中。远程攻击者可通过在恶意网页中植入特制 JavaScript 代码，监控用户跨站点的网页浏览活动，窃取用户的浏览历史与访问行为等敏感信息。该漏洞由贝尔实验室发现并报告，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低，但由于浏览器版本较早且已停止支持，实际利用价值有限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0031"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:23.630","remediation":"立即停止使用 Internet Explorer 3.x/4.x 及 Netscape 2.x/3.x/4.x，升级到受支持的主流浏览器（如 Chrome、Edge、Firefox 最新版本），这些浏览器已不存在该跨域脚本监控漏洞。对于无法升级浏览器的老旧系统，建议在终端安装脚本拦截插件（如 NoScript）并禁用 JavaScript 执行作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.codetalker.com/advisories/vendor/hp/hpsbux9707-065.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0093.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0092","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0092.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0030","title":"SGI IRIX xlock 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 系统及其他类 Unix 操作系统（包括 BSD/OS、DG/UX、Debian、HP-UX、IBM AIX、Solaris）中 xlock 屏幕锁定程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可利用该漏洞向 xlock 发送特制输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响广泛的多款 Unix 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0030"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:23.497","remediation":"SGI IRIX 系统应立即升级 xlock 程序至厂商已修复版本（如 IRIX 6.4 对应安全补丁），其他受影响系统（BSD/OS 2.1、Debian 1.3、HP-UX 10.34、IBM AIX 4.2、Solaris 2.5.1 等）应从各自厂商获取 xlock 安全更新。若无法立即打补丁，作为临时缓解措施可移除 xlock 的 setuid root 权限位（执行 chmod u-s /usr/bin/X11/xlock），限制本地用户以提权方式运行 xlock 程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0030"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0092.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0091","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0091.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0028","title":"SGI IRIX login/scheme 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 系统的 login/scheme 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞通过向存在缺陷的命令提交超长输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取系统 root 权限。该漏洞影响多个 SGI IRIX 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有系统本地访问权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0028"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-07-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:23.163","remediation":"SGI IRIX 5.3/6.2/6.3/6.4/6.5 均受影响，应立即安装 SGI 对应版本的安全补丁（如 IRIX 6.5 安装 Patch 3180 或更新版本）。若无法立即打补丁，可执行 `chmod u-s /usr/sbin/scheme` 移除 scheme 命令的 setuid 位，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0028"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0091.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0090","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0090.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0034","title":"Perl suidperl 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"suidperl（sperl）是 Perl 中用于执行 SUID 权限脚本的辅助程序，其在处理用户输入时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向目标系统提交特制的 Perl 脚本参数触发该溢出，覆盖内存中的关键数据结构，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Perl 4.x 及 5.x 版本，涉及 BSD/OS、RedHat、SGI 等多个操作系统平台，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0034"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:24.680","remediation":"升级 Perl 至 5.004 或更高版本以修复 suidperl 缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，可移除 suidperl 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/suidperl），并改用 sudo 机制替代 setuid 脚本执行。长期建议彻底废弃 suidperl，使用常规 Perl 解释器配合 sudo 调用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0034","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19547","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0034.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0034","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0034.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0034.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0034.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6v5q-h64v-p5mp/GHSA-6v5q-h64v-p5mp.json","https://github.com/briandfoy/cpan-security-advisory/blob/b45d5ed44c1ca4a46a9138ebed1f2bec6deb0956/TO_DO","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0034.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0090.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0090.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0090.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0089","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0089.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0029","title":"SGI IRIX ordist 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 5.3 及 6.2 系统中的 ordist 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可向 ordist 命令提交特制请求触发缓冲区越界读取，从而获取系统 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 5.3 和 6.2 版本，利用前提是攻击者拥有本地系统访问权限，属于本地权限提升漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0029"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-07-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:23.303","remediation":"安装 SGI 于 1997 年发布的 ordist 安全补丁（SGI Security Advisory 19970701），或升级到 IRIX 6.3 及以上版本。如无法升级，建议移除 ordist 的 setuid root 权限：chmod u-s /usr/sbin/ordist，并限制仅授信用户可本地登录系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0029","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19317","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0029.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0029","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f47735aa52980ccd9473eed79b62a27c199a2cfa/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0029.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0029.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0029.md","https://github.com/krafthack-by-techday/Night-s-watch/blob/30ae1bcc335306fe4c5507b2c629cae4932e515e/cve/nvd/CVE-1999-0029_0f0c3530-7572-4860-a943-991d78115c24","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-65pf-462r-g52c/GHSA-65pf-462r-g52c.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0029.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0089.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0089.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0089.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0087","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0087.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0430","title":"Cisco Catalyst系列交换机 Supervisor软件 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cisco Catalyst 系列交换机（涵盖 2900/1200/5000 系列）的 Supervisor 软件存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标交换机发送特制数据包，强制 Supervisor 模块重载，导致设备服务中断。该漏洞影响 Catalyst 2900/1200/5000 系列交换机，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危，攻击者可通过网络远程触发，无需特殊权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0430"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:22.743","remediation":"升级 Cisco Catalyst 5000 系列交换机 Supervisor 模块软件至修复版本。Cisco 已发布包含补丁的 Catalyst 5000 Supervisor 软件更新，请通过 Cisco.com 下载并安装最新版本。对于已结束生命周期的旧型号，建议尽快迁移至 Cisco Catalyst 9000 系列交换机以消除风险。临时缓解措施可在管理接口 ACL 中限制 SNMP/Telnet 访问来源 IP，仅允许受信任管理网段。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1103"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0087.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0085","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0085.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0428","title":"OpenSSL SSLeay SSL 会话重用及访问控制绕过漏洞","description":"OpenSSL 及 SSLeay 存在 SSL 会话重用漏洞，远程攻击者可利用已建立的 SSL 会话绕过访问控制机制，从而未授权访问受保护的资源。该漏洞源于 SSL/TLS 协议实现中会话缓存管理缺陷，允许攻击者重用已认证的会话标识符，导致权限验证被绕过。无需认证即可远程利用，影响 OpenSSL 及 SSLeay 多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0428"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:22.500","remediation":"升级 OpenSSL 到 0.9.2b 或更高版本。0.9.2b 修复了 SSL session 重用绕过访问控制的缺陷。如无法升级，可在应用层强制每次 TLS 握手使用新 session ID，并禁用 session 缓存复用功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/3936"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0085.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0084","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0084.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0427","title":"Qualcomm Eudora 邮件客户端长文件名附件拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Eudora 4.1 邮件客户端在处理附件文件名时存在缓冲区边界检查缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送包含超长文件名的恶意邮件附件触发此漏洞。当 Eudora 尝试解析或显示过长的文件名时，会导致邮件客户端崩溃或拒绝服务，影响 Eudora 系列产品的正常使用。攻击者无需身份认证即可实施攻击，但需要诱导用户接收并打开邮件。此漏洞 CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0427"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:22.377","remediation":"升级到 Eudora 4.2 或更高版本，该版本限制附件文件名长度，避免超长文件名导致的拒绝服务。由于 Eudora 已停止维护，建议迁移至 Thunderbird 等现代邮件客户端以持续获得安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0427"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0084.toml"}]